video_info.title: WATCH: Trump rally FULL SPEECH at St Cloud campaign event | LiveNOW from FOX
video_info.description:
Former president Donald Trump, as well as his running mate JD Vance, focused heavily on crime, the economy and immigration during the event held in St. Cloud, Minnesota.

"President Donald Trump is devastated to see the path of death and destruction left behind by Democrats and their activist friends. President Trump will ease the financial pressures placed on households and re-establish law and order in Minnesota!" Trump's pre-rally campaign post read in part.
